In re Resignation of Friedman.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Friedman (1993), 67 Ohio St.3d 1204.]

(No. 93-1286 Submitted July 8, 1993 Decided July 9, 1993.)

The resignation of Jules K. Friedman of Cincinnati, Ohio, as an attorney, Registration No. 0025573, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
